m>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/longjourney" target="_blank">longjourney</a>)</em></strong> - <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:the-journal-of-aframos-longjourney">《Aframos Longjourney游记》</a></li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E8%A1%8C%E8%80%85%E6%B8%B8%E8%AE%B0" target="_blank">行者游记</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/journal-of-the-walk" target="_blank">journal-of-the-walk</a>)</em></strong> - <a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:journal-of-the-walk">《行者游记》</a></li> </ul> <hr /> <h2><span>中文原创典籍</span></h2> <p><strong>如果你想要申请一个新的原创典籍标签，请先阅读<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:the-library-cn">原创图书馆中心页下方的写作指导</a>，然后在该页的讨论区发帖申请，包括现有作品及简要介绍。</strong></p> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E8%8B%8D%E6%A0%91%E4%B8%8E%E8%A1%80" target="_blank">苍树与血</a></strong> - 《苍树与血》</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%81%BE%E5%85%BD%E6%A2%A6%E8%AF%AD" target="_blank">灾兽梦语</a></strong> - 《灾兽梦语》</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E6%A2%A6%E4%B9%8B%E8%B0%8F%E8%A8%80" target="_blank">梦之谏言</a></strong> - 《梦之谏言》</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E6%AC%A2%E5%A3%B0%E7%AC%91%E8%AF%AD" target="_blank">欢声笑语</a></strong> - 《欢声笑语》</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%81%B0%E7%83%AC%E6%AE%8B%E9%A1%B5" target="_blank">灰烬残页</a></strong> - 《灰烬残页》</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E6%B8%B8%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%97%E5%BC%82" target="_blank">游人志异</a></strong> - 《游人志异》</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%90%85%E5%AC%9B%E7%A6%8F%E5%9C