/%E7%84%9A%E4%B9%A6%E4%BA%BA" target="_blank">焚书人</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/bookburners" target="_blank">bookburners</a>)</em></strong> - 相关组织焚书人，或称全球超自然联盟。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%8B%82%E4%BA%BA" target="_blank">狂人</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/madmen" target="_blank">madmen</a>)</em></strong> - 相关组织狂人，或称混沌分裂者。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA" target="_blank">商人</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/merchants" target="_blank">merchants</a>)</em></strong> - 相关组织商人，或称 Marshall, Carter和Dark有限公司。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E8%9B%87%E6%89%8B" target="_blank">蛇手</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/serpents-hand" target="_blank">serpents-hand</a>)</em></strong> - 部分或全部由一名蛇之手成员所写就的文章，或者含蓄或明确地提及蛇之手的文章。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/legacy" target="_blank">legacy</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/legacy" target="_blank">legacy</a>)</em></strong> - 组织“Legacy”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/neverwere" target="_blank">neverwere</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/neverwere" target="_blank">neverwere</a>)</em></strong> - 相关组织Neverwere。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/planasthai" target="_blank">planasthai</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/planasthai" target="_blank">planasthai</a>)</em></strong> - 出版物“<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:from-the-editor-s-desk">the Planasthai</a>”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%91%98" target="_blank">图书管理员</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/librarians" target="_blank">librarians</a>)</em></strong> - 实体“图书管理员”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E8%80%81%E8%A1%A8%E9%98%BF%E4%B8%B9" target="_blank">老表阿丹</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/cousin-dan" target="_blank">cousin-dan</a>)</em></strong> - 人物“老表阿丹”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ulak" target="_blank">ulak</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ulak" target="_blank">ulak</a>)</em></strong> - 人物“漫游者Ulak”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E9%A6%86" target="_blank">图书馆</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/library" target="_blank">library</a>)</em></strong> - 与图书馆本身有关的文章。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/elrich" target="_blank">elrich</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/elrich" target="_blank">elrich</a>)</em></strong> - 地点或领域“Elrich”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/unwaking" target="_blank">unwaking</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/unwaking" target="_blank">unwaking</a>)</em></strong> - 世界或地点“the Unwaking”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/yoren" target="_blank">yoren</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/yoren" target="_blank">yoren</a>)</em></strong> - 世界或地点“Yoren”。</li> </ul> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-4" style="display:none"> <h2><span>特性标签</span></h2> <p>有关特定概念、构思或特性的标签。一篇文章可以有多个特性标签，也可以完全没有！</p> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E8%B4%B5%E6%97%8F" target="_blank">贵族</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/aristocratic" target="_blank">aristocratic</a>)</em></strong> - 与皇室、贵族或类似阶层有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%A5%A5%E7%A7%98%E6%A4%8D%E7%89%A9" target="_blank">奥秘植物</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/cryptobotanical" target="_blank">cryptobotanical</a>)</em></strong> - 与某种未曾被正式记载或者超自然的植物有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%A5%A5%E7%A7%98%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9" target="_blank">奥秘动物</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/cryptozoological" target="_blank">cryptozoological</a>)</em></strong> - 与某种未曾被公开记载或者超自然的动物有关。请勿与“<strong>异界</strong>”混淆，后者代表通过密径连接的其他世界。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%A5%9E%E7%81%B5" target="_blank">神灵</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/divine" target="_blank">divine</a>)</em></strong> - 与神灵起源或能力相关的个体、物体或概念有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93" target="_blank">个体</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/entity" target="_blank">entity</a>)</em></strong> - 与一个超自然的独立个体有关，而不是表现得像一堆有机体的东西。能被“<strong>奥秘植物</strong>”或“<strong>奥秘动物</strong>”取代。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E4%B8%9B%E6%9E%97" target="_blank">丛林</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/forest" target="_blank">forest</a>)</em></strong> - 与特定丛林有关，或者发生于丛林的故事。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2" target="_blank">历史</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/historical" target="_blank">historical</a>)</em></strong> - 与知名的历史重要事件有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA" target="_blank">地区</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/location" target="_blank">location</a>)</em></strong> - 与一个具有特别意义的地理区域有关。已有“设定标签”的区域不再需要“<strong>地区</strong>”标签。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%86%9B%E9%98%9F" target="_blank">军队</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/military" target="_blank">military</a>)</em></strong> - 与一支军事力量或者该军事力量的某次行动——例如战争——有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D" target="_blank">神话</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/" target="_blank">mythological</a>)</em></strong> - 与现有的神话、传说或故事有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93" target="_blank">物体</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/object" target="_blank">object</a>)</em></strong> - 与某种超自然或者具有重要现实意义的物体有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%BC%82%E7%95%8C" target="_blank">异界</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/otherworldly" target="_blank">otherworldly</a>)</em></strong> - 与一个或多个其他宇宙世界有关。注意图书馆本身并不能算是一个世界。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E6%80%A7" target="_blank">宗教性</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/religion" target="_blank">religion</a>)</em></strong> - 与某个特定的宗教及其习俗或信仰有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E4%BB%AA%E5%BC%8F" target="_blank">仪式</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ritual" target="_blank">ritual</a>)</em></strong> - 与某种由一个或多个有智力的团体所进行的仪式性且可靠的过程有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA" target="_blank">太空</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/space" target="_blank">space</a>)</em></strong> - 与被称作“太空”的真空空间有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E9%AC%BC%E7%81%B5" target="_blank">鬼灵</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/spirit" target="_blank">spirit</a>)</em></strong> - 与被称作“鬼灵”的个体有关，例如鬼魂、幽灵和恶魔。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD" target="_blank">部落</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/tribal" target="_blank">tribal</a>)</em></strong> - 与某种由人类或类人生物所组成的、部落形式的、有组织的社会团体。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%AF%86%E5%BE%84" target="_blank">密径</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ways" target="_blank">ways</a>)</em></strong> - 与一种被称之为“<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:the-universe#toc4">密径</a>”的现象有关。</li> </ul> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-5" style="display:none"> <h2><span>竞赛标签</span></h2> <p>用于官方竞赛的标签。</p> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/wlc2013" target="_blank">wlc2013</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/wlc2013" target="_blank">wlc2013</a>)</em></strong> - <a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:first-annual-wanderer-s-library-writing-contest-ar">2013被放逐者之图书馆竞赛</a>。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%AB%9E%E8%B5%9B" target="_blank">生活竞赛</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/life-contest" target="_blank">life-contest</a>)</em></strong> - 首页征文“<a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:fictionalized-life-stories-contest">虚构的生活故事</a>”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/wanderlust01" target="_blank">wanderlust01</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/wanderlust01" target="_blank">wanderlust01</a>)</em></strong> - 第一期首页征文“迷失”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/spacewitch02" target="_blank">spacewitch02</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/spacewitch02" target="_blank">spacewitch02</a>)</em></strong> - 第二期首页征文“太空巫师”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/relationship03" target="_blank">relationship03</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/relationship03" target="_blank">relationship03</a>)</em></strong> - 第三期首页征文“联系”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/cities04" target="_blank">cities04</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/cities04" target="_blank">cities04</a>)</em></strong> - 第四期首页征文“城市”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/altplaces05" target="_blank">altplaces05</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/altplaces05" target="_blank">altplaces05</a>)</em></strong> - 第五期首页征文“平行世界”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/whyandwho06" target="_blank">whyandwho06</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/whyandwho06" target="_blank">whyandwho06</a>)</em></strong> - 第六期首页征文“何与谁”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/creatures07" target="_blank">creatures07</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/creatures07" target="_blank">creatures07</a>)</em></strong> - 第七期首页征文“生物”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/av08" target="_blank">av08</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/av08" target="_blank">av08</a>)</em></strong> - 第八期首页征文“影音”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ws2019" target="_blank">ws2019</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ws2019" target="_blank">ws2019</a>)</em></strong> - <a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:the-wanderer-s-station">2019流浪者站竞赛</a>。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/wd2020" target="_blank">wd2020</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/wd2020" target="_blank">wd2020</a>)</em></strong> - <a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:wanderers-depths-contest">2020被放逐者的深潜竞赛</a>。</li> </ul> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-6" style="display:none"> <h2><span>已归档的标签</span></h2> <p>这些标签曾用于图书馆，但由于种种原因现已归档、不再使用。<strong>这些标签不应该用于任何新创作的作品中。</strong></p> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/swedenborg" target="_blank">swedenborg</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/swedenborg" target="_blank">swedenborg</a>)</em></strong> - 伪斯韦登伯格（the False Swedenborg）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/pangur" target="_blank">pangur</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/pangur" target="_blank">pangur</a>)</em></strong> - 潘古尔（Pangur）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/redtooth" target="_blank">redtooth</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/redtooth" target="_blank">redtooth</a>)</em></strong> - 艾米莉·红齿（Emily Redtooth）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/thorn" target="_blank">thorn</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/thorn" target="_blank">thorn</a>)</em></strong> - 荆棘顽童（the Thorn Child）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ilvos" target="_blank">ilvos</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ilvos" target="_blank">ilvos</a>)</em></strong> - 锈蚀骑士团的艾尔沃斯（Ilvos of the Rusted Blade）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/bogg" target="_blank">bogg</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/bogg" target="_blank">bogg</a>)</em></strong> - 阿格奈什·博格（Agnes Bogg）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/kragg" target="_blank">kragg</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/kragg" target="_blank">kragg</a>)</em></strong> - 恐惧飞龙克拉（the Dread Wyrm Kragg）书架。</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mscarlet" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1745583&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610223150" alt="MScarlet" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1745583)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mscarlet" >MScarlet</a></span></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">脚注</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-683387-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. 部分语言分部仍使用“<strong>未分级</strong>”标签，注意在翻译时需要修改为“<strong>机密分级</strong>”。</div> </div> 
