					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><sub><strong>&#171;</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/aiad-homescreen">HUB</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/alert-lockdown-initiated">第一部份</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/command-query-separation">第二部份</a> | <span style="color: blue">第三部份: 超加密</span> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/clock-multiplier">第四部份</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/null-terminating-string">第五部份</a> <strong>&#187;</strong></sub></p> </div> <hr /> <p><br /> <br /></p> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>你找我嗎？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex4.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex4.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <br /> <br /> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>Alexandra，Site-17已經失聯了。你在最近幾小時裡能連上嗎？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <br /> <br /> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>我先前沒試過。他們已經失聯多久了？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex_sad.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <br /> <br /> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>三小時而已，但能足以排除通信錯誤了。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <br /> <br /> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>Glacon沒表示些什麼嗎？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex_sad.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <br /> <br /> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>沒。幫我個忙，看看你能否透過其他途徑把封包交給他。可以嗎？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <br /> <br /> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; wi