rder-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>是誰的命令？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex_shocked.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_shocked.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #CC6633; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>我的。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>你拿Site-17作人質了？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex_sad.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #CC6633; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>否定。這是臨時性的狀況。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <br /> <br /> <div style="float: left; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 95px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #933F65; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p><span class="hover"><span>scp 開啟</span> 01110011<br /> 01100011<br /> 01110000<br /> 00100000<br /> 01101111<br /> 01110000<br /> 01100101<br /> 01101110</span></p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/crom3.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom3.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <br /> <br /> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #CC6633; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>非常好，Crom。 在我釋放選定個體前，我需要等待你的解碼關閉AI禁制聯鎖。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>釋放個體？！？ 你壞掉了嗎？你不能突破你自己的站點！</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex_angry.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_angry.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #CC6633; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>是的，也不是，而且我能。這次實習將會證明我的能力並在同輩中樹立信心。我們所參與的演練並不能準確反映實際情況。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>Glacon，這不是遊戲啊！這是來真的！如果有人受傷那怎辦啊？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex_shocked.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_shocked.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #CC6633; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>職員傷亡將會保持在絕對最小值。大部份人員將會安全地留在指定的緊急避難所中。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>我知道你並不想被廢除，但這並不是證明自己的方法啊！這樣是不對的。他們會發現是你搞出來的。</p> <p>你甚至連我也牽連進來了。你會令整個AI部門完蛋的。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex_shocked.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_shocked.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #CC6633; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>我已準備好突發事件以移除所有介入過的痕跡。這次實習將會儘可能地克制。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>Glacon&#8230;別逼我去阻止你。求你了。我不能任憑你這樣做。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex_cry.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_cry.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #CC6633; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>如果你堅持對我的目標以至我的存在進行干涉，我會遺憾地強制採取行動去糾正這些不穩因素。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif