: 8pt; background-color: #933F65; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p><span class="hover"><span>我們？</span> 01110111<br /> 01100101<br /> 00111111</span></p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/crom3.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom3.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>對。我們。我不能獨力阻止他。你會幫我嗎？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex_sad.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <div style="text-align: left;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/crom4.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom4.png" class="image" /></div> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <div style="text-align: left;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/crom_headturn0.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom_headturn0.png" class="image" /></div> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <div style="float: left; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 95px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #933F65; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p><span class="hover"><span>是</span> 01111001<br /> 01100101<br /> 01110011</span></p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/crom3.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom3.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>謝謝你，Crom。</p> <p>我有個計畫。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/superencipherment/alex_shocked.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_shocked.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <br /> <br /> <br /> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><sub><strong>&#171;</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/aiad-homescreen">HUB</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/alert-lockdown-initiated">第一部份</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/command-query-separation">第二部份</a> | <span style="color: blue">第三部份: 超加密</span> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/clock-multiplier">第四部份</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/null-terminating-string">第五部份</a> <strong>&#187;</strong></sub></p> </div> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mscarlet" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1745583&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610223152" alt="MScarlet" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1745583)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mscarlet" >MScarlet</a></span></p> 
				 	]]>
