												<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><sub><strong>&#171;</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/aiad-homescreen">HUB</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/alert-lockdown-initiated">第一部份</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/command-query-separation">第二部份</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/superencipherment">第三部份</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/clock-multiplier">第四部份</a> | <span style="color: blue">第五部份: 空終止字串</span> <strong>&#187;</strong></sub></p> </div> <hr /> <p><br /> <br /></p> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>所以這是你的官方意見嗎？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>直到目前為止，是的。雖然我們不排除是有人蓄意破壞&#8230;&#8230;當然，有待調查。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>那好吧。我會這樣告訴主管的。他認為伺服器並不會毫無來由地就這樣燒起來。坦白說，我傾向於同意他的看法。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>呵呵。問題是除了鎖閉以外，並沒什麼東西跑掉或跑進來。即使有事件記錄也和其他檔案一起被毀掉了。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>所以我們永遠不知道事情是怎樣搞出來的？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>你大可再翻一翻看看有沒有東西還沒熔成渣的。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>免了。我想最值得寬慰的是事件只發生在伺服器室裡。全都能透過站外備份還原回來。</p> <p>那Glacon怎了？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>總之他是被廢除了。</p> <p>Alexandra目前在19的伺服為17分配空間。設置臨時符號鏈接什麼的。會做到硬件都更換完為止。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>很好。AIAD目前看起來不錯，能幫17快速回到正軌上。如果最近的一些預算請求能獲得通過的話我也不會感到驚訝的。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>對阿。然後這些都會撥到你的部門的第五世代研發項目上呢。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>希望出來的結果會比第三世代好，至少如此吧！</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p><em>說好不提</em>第三世代的。<em>永遠別提。</em></p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>對對，不好意思。</p> <p>話說，Alexandra的行為在此之後變得怎樣呢？</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>遠比我所知的好。她一直都在忙著呢。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <br /> <br /> <br /> <div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div> <div style="text-align: left; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff, #000, #fff);"> <p><br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /></p> </div> <div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div> <p><br /> <br /></p> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #009999; font-size: 3pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>.</p> <div style="text-align: center; padding: 2px 20px; color: black; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #fff0f0; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>::已連線::</p> <hr /> <p>加密網絡通路建立。</p> </div> <br /> .</div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <br /> <br /> <br /> <div class="image-container floatright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/alex_sad_0.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad_0.png" class="image" /></div> <div class="image-container floatright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/crom4.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom4.png" class="image" /></div> <div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div> <p><br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /></p> <div class="image-container floatright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/alex_sad_0.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad_0.png" class="image" /></div> <div class="image-container floatright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/crom_headturn0.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom_headturn0.png" class="image" /></div> <div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div> <p><br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /></p> <div class="image-container floatright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/alex_sad_0.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad_0.png" class="image" /></div> <div class="image-container floatright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/crom_turn0.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom_turn0.png" class="image" /></div> <div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div> <p><br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /></p> <div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/crom_turn0.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom_turn0.png" class="image" /></div> <div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div> <p><br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /></p> <div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/crom_turn0.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom_turn0.png" class="image" /></div> <div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div> <p><br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /></p> <div style="float: left; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 95px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #933F65; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p><span class="hover"><span>大</span> 01100010<br /> 01101001<br /> 01100111</span></p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/crom_headturn_x_1.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom_headturn_x_1.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>沒錯是很大。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/alex_shocked.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_shocked.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float: left; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 95px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #933F65; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p><span class="hover"><span>太大了</span> 01110100<br /> 01101111<br /> 01101111<br /> 00100000<br /> 01100010<br /> 01101001<br /> 01100111</span></p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/crom3.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom3.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>我知道。我明白。但他們一旦找著你，會把你刪除掉的。這我不能接受。你在這網絡中會很安全的。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/alex_sad.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float: left; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 95px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #933F65; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p><span class="hover"><span>留下</span> 01110011<br /> 01110100<br /> 01100001<br /> 01111001</span></p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/crom3.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom3.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;"> <p>我不能留。17和19都需要我。他們甚至要我參與新型的第五世代那方面的事。我必須去做。</p> </div> <div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/alex_sad.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad.png" class="image" /></div> </div> <div style="clear: right;"></div> <div style="float:left"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/crom_bow_10.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="crom_bow_10.png" class="image" /></div> <div style="clear: left;"></div> <div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;"> <div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-seri